@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home";
}

<div class="row align-items-center g-4">
    <div class="col-lg-7">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">Playing Soccer</h1>
        <p class="lead">
            Soccer is my favorite hobby because it’s competitive, social, and always pushes me to improve.
            I love how it blends endurance, speed, strategy, and teamwork.
        </p>

        <p>
            One of the best parts of soccer is how there’s always something to work on—first touch, passing,
            finishing, defending, positioning, and decision-making under pressure.
        </p>

        <p>
            Beyond skills, soccer is great for mental toughness. You learn to stay calm, communicate clearly,
            and adapt quickly when the game changes. Whether it’s a casual pickup match or a serious game day,
            it’s always a good time.
        </p>

        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Calculator">
            Estimate Tutoring Cost
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-5">
        <div class="card shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="h5 mb-3">Game Day Vibes</h2>

                <img src="~/images/soccer1.png" class="hobby-img mb-3" alt="Soccer image 1" />
                <img src="~/images/soccer2.png" class="hobby-img" alt="Soccer image 2" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
